Multiple award-winning singer Davido has announced plans to give out N20million to 20 people on Friday. The music star made the announcement via his Twitter handle on Wednesday. He explained he desired to assist the specified number of persons beginning a business seeing how tough things are in the country.   Most dangerous thing about Nigeria, by Simi     Ifuennada curses celebrities campaigning for ‘useless…     Tonto Dikeh to fans: unfollow me if…   The DMW boss encouraged persons with great business/startup ideas to send them to him to stand a chance to benefit from his philanthropic gesture. Davido tweeted: “Country hard right now sha … let’s give 20m to 20 pple on Friday … send in your business ideas or start-up ideas … more details shortly #Wrblo.” In another tweet, he said: “Govt don fail us nah to dey help each other we dey now.”